<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4071731>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Limois westwoodii (Hope, 1843), Myanmar, Nat Ma Taung, RBINS, adult male. A. Dorsal view. B. Head and thorax, dorsal view. C. Ventral view. D. Face. E. Left lateral view. F. Head and thorax, left lateral view (showing reflexed protuberance of the vertex). Photographs by J. Constant." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4071731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4071733>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Limois westwoodii (Hope, 1843) holotype, adult female. A. Dorsal view. B. Head and thorax, dorsal view. C. Labels. D, F. Face. E. Ventral view. G. Right lateral view. H. Head and thorax, right lateral view (showing reflexed protuberance of the vertex). Photographs by K. Child." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4071733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4071723>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Limois kikuchii Kato, 1932, Manchuria, K. Kikuchi leg., RBINS, adult male. A. Dorsal view. B. Head and thorax, dorsal view. C. Face. D. Ventral view. E. Head and thorax, right lateral view (showing reflexed protuberance of the vertex). F. Right lateral view. G. Labels. Photographs by J. Constant." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4071723/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4071735>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Limois westwoodii (Hope, 1843), Myanmar, Nat Ma Taung, RBINS, male genitalia. A. Left lateral view (except phallic complex). B. Gonostylus, ventral view. C. Anal tube, dorsal view. D–F. Aedeagus. D. Dorsal view. E. Ventral view. F. Left lateral view. Photographs by J. Constant." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4071735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4071751>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Distribution map for species of Limois Stal, 1863." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4071751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

